stories.title: 4th ODI, India v Zimbabwe, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1659th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: Bengal players rush to Ganguly's defence
stories.summary:
The one-match ban that has been enforced by match
referee Barry Jarman on the Indian captain Sourav
Ganguly has come in for criticism from some of
leading cricketers in Calcutta

stories.title: The Indian skipper did just about everything right
stories.summary:
Sourav Ganguly had made it very clear that his bowlers have been found
wanting during this series against Zimbabwe

stories.title: Ganguly, Dahiya served notices for showing dissent
stories.summary:
Captain Saurav Ganguly's sterling all-round performance in India's
crushing nine-wicket victory over Zimbabwe in the fourth one-dayer in
Kanpur today was blotted after match referee Barry Jarman served
notices on him and wicket-keeper Vijay Dahiya

stories.title: Ganguly fashions series victory
stories.summary:
India clinched the five match India Zimbabwe one
day series with a fine nine wicket win at the
Green Park stadium in Kanpur on Monday
